1. Requirements
---------------

- The following external programs are mandatory in order to compile Fittino

  ROOT   (http://root.cern.ch/drupal)
  slhaea (http://fthomas.github.com/slhaea)

2. Installation
---------------

- Change to the build directory

  cd build

- In order to configure cmake type

  cmake ..

- To build Fittino type

  make

  or

  make install

  to install it in a directory specified in CMakeList.txt

- If the compilation is successful an executable called "fittino" is produced in
  build/sources/kernel
